==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Douroucouli
<hw>Dou`rou*cou"li</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small, nocturnal, South American monkey of the
genus <gen>Aotus</gen> (formerly <spn>Nyctipithecus trivirgatus</spn>),
with large owl-like eyes; hence, the common name <altname>owl
monkey</altname>.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>Durukuli</asp> and
<asp>dourikuli</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source> ]</p>

<p><ent>Douse</ent>⟦br⟧
